🕸️ AI Web Scraper
This project is an AI-powered web scraper that enables users to extract and parse specific information from websites using natural language instructions.

✨ Features
Web Scraping: Extracts content from any given URL.
Text Cleaning: Removes unnecessary HTML elements and formats the extracted content.
AI-Powered Parsing: Utilizes the Ollama language model to interpret user instructions and extract relevant information.
User-Friendly Interface: Built with Streamlit for easy interaction.

🛠️ How It Works
Input: The user enters a URL to scrape.
Scraping: The application scrapes the website and cleans the extracted text.
Instruction: The user provides a description of the information they want to extract.
Parsing: The AI model parses the content based on the user's instructions and returns the relevant information.

⚙️ Requirements
Python 3.7+
Libraries:
Streamlit
Langchain
Langchain Ollama
Selenium
BeautifulSoup4
ChromeDriver: Ensure ChromeDriver is installed and accessible for Selenium.

🚀 Installation
Clone this repository:
git clone https://github.com/mbs2222/AI-Web-Scraper.git
cd AI-Web-Scraper
Install the required packages:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Ensure ChromeDriver is installed and its path is correctly set in scrape.py.

🖥️ Usage
Run the Streamlit app:
streamlit run main.py
Scrape a Site:
Enter a URL and click "Scrape Site".
Parse Content:
Enter a description of the desired content and click "Parse Content".

📁 Project Files
main.py: The main Streamlit application.
scrape.py: Functions for web scraping and text cleaning.
parse.py: Manages AI-powered parsing using Ollama.

📝 Note
This project uses the Ollama language model. Make sure it is properly set up and running on your system.

